==English==

[[Image:Colossus_of_Rhodes.jpg|right|250px|The Colossus of Rhodes in a 16th-century engraving by Martin Heemskerck]]

===Proper noun===
{{en-proper noun}}

# a [[gigantic]] [[bronze]] [[statue]] of [[Helios]] built at [[Rhodes]] under the direction of the sculptor [[w:Chares of Lindos|Chares]] (Greek [[Χάρης]] or Χαρής); one of the [[w:Seven Wonders of the World|Seven Wonders of the Ancient World]].

